# Editable files — shipped as *.template, copied to live filename on
# first bootstrap. Live filenames stay out of git so daily `git pull`
# never collides with user edits. See §6e of the v2 plan.
USER.md
IDENTITY.md
TONE.md
WORKSTYLE.md
CURRENT.md
onboarding/company.md
onboarding/team.md
onboarding/role.md
packs/team-*.md
packs/personal-*.md
!packs/team-*.md.template
!packs/personal-*.md.template

.DS_Store
